    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-05-20T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-05-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="894"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d894">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-05-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 662.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inclose herewith a copy,
                    together with a translation, of a note that has been received from the ministry
                    of state in connection with the taking of oath of His Majesty King Alfonso XIII,
                    informing this legation in official form of that act.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stanton Sickles.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure.—Translation.]</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Duke of Almodóvar del Rio</gloss>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Sickles</persName>.</hi>
                    </head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Ministry of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                    >Madrid</hi>
                            </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-05-17">
                                <hi rend="italic">May 17, 1902</hi>
                            </date>.</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Sir</hi>: It is with extreme satisfaction that
                        I announce to you that His Majesty the King my august sovereign, who has
                        arrived at his majority, has just taken oath to the constitution of the
                        state in the form prescribed by the fundamental law of Spain, and that the
                        Spanish Monarchy reigns from to-day.</p>
                    <p>In giving you official news of such a memorable and happy event, I repeat the
                        assurance, etc.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">The Duke of Almodóvar del Rio.</hi>
                    </closer>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
